Class DescribeHostsRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.AmazonWebServiceRequest
      • com.amazonaws.services.ec2.model.DescribeHostsRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    public class DescribeHostsRequest
extends AmazonWebServiceRequest
implements java.io.Serializable
    Container for the parameters to the DescribeHosts operation.

    Describes one or more of your Dedicated hosts.

    The results describe only the Dedicated hosts in the region you're currently using. All listed instances consume capacity on your Dedicated host. Dedicated hosts that have recently been released will be listed with the state released .

    See Also:
    AmazonEC2.describeHosts(DescribeHostsRequest), Serialized Form
